{
  "id": "RAW_214999b8",
  "title": "开源即爆火！英伟达重磅推出 OmniVinci 全模态大模型",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651000328&idx=3&sn=6e0c61c7e00c38f62904bc9b74748282",
  "date": "2025-11-06 05:26:00",
  "author": "机器之心",
  "siteName": "机器之心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">全模态智能，英伟达的下一步</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">你是否想过，未来的 AI 将会是什么样子？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">是只会打字的 Chat Bot，只会看图的 VLM，还是只能分辨声音的 ALM？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">都不是！ 真正的智能，应该像我们人类一样，能够同时</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">看、听、说、写</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，既能看懂世界的五彩斑斓，也能听懂万物的声音。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503516507\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6444444444444445\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=326f18ee&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicBLKeEFCnStqlc7nuRDNjso6MsTgxGMYVh6kMXpaNrLoAHGht3IG9QcIgkQdbmAOyQjPb2MngVfA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在不久前结束的英伟达华盛顿 GTC 大会上，老黄再三强调 “</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">研究人员需要开源。开发者依赖开源。全球的公司，包括我们都离不开开源模型。开源非常，非常，重要。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">” 在老黄的号召下，全模态理解模型迎来重量级新玩家 —— 英伟达（NVIDIA）开源了 OmniVinci, 一款能理解多模态世界的全模态大语言模型（Omni-Modal LLM）。该模型实现了视觉、音频、语言在同一潜空间（latent space）中的统一理解， 让 AI 不仅能识别图像、听懂语音，还能推理、对话、生成内容。这个 9B 的视觉 - 语音理解全模态模型刚上线就爆火，一周时间 Huggingface 模型权重目前已经有超过&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">10000</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;次下载量！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503516551\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.14133900106269925\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"941\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=03690f21&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicBLKeEFCnStqlc7nuRDNjsn0bicMUQDDB2gbzEK0K9PrdIeEKuRNmsGT2IsW2Siazibuf2EytTx8NYg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503516510\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5889830508474576\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"944\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=22ca34cf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicBLKeEFCnStqlc7nuRDNjszoM8FgXIe5uu2cKRxyWH6ykY0wgEDqvbgneVPae3WFib4YYicg2ibXZng%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">论文标题：OmniVinci: Enhancing Architecture and Data for Omni-Modal Understanding LLM</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">项目地址：<a href=\"https://github.com/NVlabs/OmniVinci\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/NVlabs/OmniVinci</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">论文地址：<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2510.15870\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2510.15870</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">开源模型：<a href=\"https://huggingface.co/nvidia/omnivinci\" target=\"_blank\">https://huggingface.co/nvidia/omnivinci</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">秀翻全场！多模态理解性能全面超越</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503516511\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.33796296296296297\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9399321d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicBLKeEFCnStqlc7nuRDNjscjJ3RVaia4EibeD6jJFzoKEKdAM3FbRjMsntm9lCvHxEFBSyw37eSw5w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">和相近尺寸的全模态模型竞品相比，OmniVinci 在多项常用多模态基准测试榜单中取得了显著优势，包括</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">视频 - 音频跨模态理解任务（DailyOmni +19.05)，音频理解 (MMAR + 1.7)，和视频理解 (Video-MME +3.9)</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，展现出卓越的全模态理解能力。更重要的是，OmniVinci 少用了近 6 倍的数据量实现了超越，展现了其架构和数据引擎的卓越效率。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">三大架构创新：让视觉与听觉在同一空间共鸣</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503516512\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.4444444444444444\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=10d17fd4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicBLKeEFCnStqlc7nuRDNjs7oHxbU6Dom2SvVRaJrHtyRHfaHhvUlEPSwDeXBicRYn4ABTIk7Su5yA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">OmniVinci 不仅具备炸裂的榜单性能，其论文中通过大量科学实验探索最优全模态模型架构的方法，而不是粗暴堆叠训练数据，这种做法显然更值得借鉴。想象一下，AI 看视频时，画面（视觉）和声音（音频）是两条独立的信息流。如果模型架构对此处理不好，AI 就会 “精神分裂”。而 OmniVinci 的目标就是让它们完美同步，通过三项核心创新设计来实现：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">OmniAlignNet：跨模态语义对齐网络</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这就像一个 “超级翻译器”，让模型在同一空间中 “看得见声音，听得懂画面”。它创建了一个共享空间，通过对比学习 ，让视觉信号和音频信号能在这里用同一种 “语言” 无障碍交流，实现</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">跨模态深度对齐</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503516514\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.45\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=47038bc6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicBLKeEFCnStqlc7nuRDNjsC75MbS0icictd0N0MsZ7Dd731f8HKrZibvaBnVhVSy8IoTHibnAEu7oztQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">Temporal Embedding Grouping (TEG)：时间嵌入分组机制</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">将视觉帧与音频信号按时间戳重组，使模型能跨模态感知事件的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">相对先后关系</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。AI 终于能搞清楚，是 “先开枪再有枪声”，还是 “先有闪电再有雷声”。它通过按时间戳分组，让 AI 理解事件的先后顺序 。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503516515\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.09351851851851851\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=60e8f4cf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicBLKeEFCnStqlc7nuRDNjsvg3URPFCb3POdUAJ6HZE2omZe2jCjoCRZCzDrqtZ9KEPoSy8tBID4g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">Constrained Rotary Time Embedding (CRTE)：受约束旋转时间嵌入</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">通过时间旋转编码，模型获得</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">绝对时间</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">感知能力。AI 不仅知道 “先” 和 “后”，还知道这件事发生在视频的第 5 秒，还是第 50 秒。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503516517\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.09166666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=44e354d0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicBLKeEFCnStqlc7nuRDNjsvzF9eZ9BJ1FLFec8ctibKzWBRnIlicU4cs213ianOib0SUeOID2FTfClLw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">有了这三板斧，OmniVinci 才真正拥有了准确感知视觉，音频和时间流逝的能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">数据引擎：24M 多模态对话的背后</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503516518\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5444444444444444\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=20cfd8b2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicBLKeEFCnStqlc7nuRDNjsEBzicwqXy5mN1mC5VGCpTKqFJX5DRib6EkjzyZqroTV3cyC1qutN0xeg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">模型强度离不开数据支撑。OmniVinci 团队构建了一个庞大的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">全模态数据引擎（Omni-Modal Data Engine）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，共涵盖</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;2400 万条多模态对话样本</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，覆盖图像、视频、音频、语音四大领域。数据分布中，图像占 36%、音频与语音共占 38%、视频 11%、全模态数据 15%。其中包括两种创新的全模态学习方式：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">隐式全模态学习（Implicit Learning）&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">直接利用现有视频自带音频的问答数据，让模型在 “看视频” 的同时 “听声音”。</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">显式全模态学习（Explicit Learning）&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">通过 AI 单独生成视觉和音频模态专属的描述，再由 LLM 进行交叉修正与融合，解决了单模态模型常见的 “幻觉”（如只看画面误判语义）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">实验：打造全模态模型的关键洞察</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">[关键洞察 1] 单一模态打标 = 不靠谱！告别 “模态幻觉”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">团队发现，很多 AI 模型都有 “模态幻觉”： 只看图（视觉）：AI 看到一个深海机器人，可能会 “脑补” 说这是人类高科技的胜利 。只听声（音频）：AI 听到旁白说 “地球最深处”，可能会 “瞎猜” 说这是关于地心的纪录片 。因此一个集成了两种模态的联合字幕方法对于全面理解至关重要。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503516529\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.41574074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5dac76fb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicBLKeEFCnStqlc7nuRDNjsoNlv7py0JJ5RJs9oXd0qlLRysqCwfRusf6sTB9Iicw8OSAyibvOYpx2A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">[关键洞察 2] &nbsp;1 + 1 &gt; 2！当听觉 “点亮” 视觉</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">加上音频，模型真的变强了吗？答案是肯定的！ 团队发现，声音为视觉提供了全新的信息维度，音视频联合学习能显著提高视频的理解能力 。只用视觉 (Visual Alone) 视觉 + 音频 (隐式学习 IL) 视觉 + 音频 + 全模态数据引擎 (显式学习 EL) 结果显示 (见下表)，每增加一步，性能都在飙升！特别是加入了数据引擎的 “显式学习” 后，模型性能在多个基准上都实现了巨大飞跃。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503516530\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.36203703703703705\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b62e8129&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicBLKeEFCnStqlc7nuRDNjsExbtTzVCwR4bENkGfWLhNQEaWRgy8SjyzlMRicJpW4qt8X2vanJibOzA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">[关键洞察 3] &nbsp;王牌对王牌：当 OmniVinci 遇上 “强化学习”&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">基础模型已经这么强了，还能再进化吗？ 能！通过强化学习 (RL)！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">音频，让强化学习 “如虎添翼”！ 团队在使用 GRPO 强化学习框架时发现了一个 “隐藏 Buff”： 只给 AI 看视频（视觉）去训练，远不如 “边看边听”（视听结合）的效果好！ 如图所示，加入音频后，模型的收敛速度更快。&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503516531\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.8607350096711799\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1034\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a2a44a37&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicBLKeEFCnStqlc7nuRDNjscoibogQCC9pUV5XEmCtHetp5YN9EH9oabhb9xs4wblvCXuLb9B3n7Gw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">强强对决，OmniVinci 更胜一筹！ 在这个多模态 RL 框架下，OmniVinci 和 Qwen2.5-Omni 都能获益 。但是，OmniVinci 凭借更强的基础性能和指令跟随能力，在 15 步内就超越了 Qwen2.5-Omni 的准确率，并且格式奖励收敛速度快了 2.7 倍 ！ 最终，经过 RL 训练的 OmniVinci+RL，在所有全模态基准上再次实现全面提升！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503516532\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.46111111111111114\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1d487295&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicBLKeEFCnStqlc7nuRDNjs9FAjPKeya9OwKhw9JwJrKHbq9ecR6TdJG7kTG274efvWNtZ9wFwZag%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503516533\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.20277777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e89402c5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicBLKeEFCnStqlc7nuRDNjsWskZEv6icNLSPokmibotmXE7bj1wEXOlj8CblYrNYdneHr5JaCtKkRKQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">不止是 SOTA，是全能 Agent</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">跑分只是基础，真正的全模态 AI，必须能在真实世界 “大显身手”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">OmniVinci 做到了。研究团队用它测试了 N 个真实场景，效果非常好 ：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">场景一：联合视听感知</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">你给它一段播客视频，它不仅能看懂主持人和嘉宾的外形，更能 “听懂” 他们讨论的复杂话题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503516522\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5120370370370371\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=96cfdbcc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicBLKeEFCnStqlc7nuRDNjsicUsWuXEEibNhoLy65iaNNUoonXecO2p39JRXV9YMY48GXfUxwkN5fpog%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">场景二：语音转录 + 翻译&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">你对它说话，它能瞬间转录成文字。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503516523\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.3685185185185185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3d4a8918&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicBLKeEFCnStqlc7nuRDNjs3uyGbmPBJfXIcStUf0AvlOPIHJ54sx0RHuOFPHWZXia38gkIrkt1lgw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">场景三：全语音交互</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">你用语音问：“这个演讲者的公司使命是啥？”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">它立刻用语音答：“他的公司使命是在火星上建立一个自我维持的文明。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503516524\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5555555555555556\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bad7d642&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicBLKeEFCnStqlc7nuRDNjsviagNQNuSt2MyP2daic1UShXoXtstNwGgzE5Zylprt4nQZaJegMBpuuw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">场景四：指挥机器人，直接 “张嘴说”！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">OmniVinci 能直接听懂你的语音指令（比如 “进入卧室，在床脚站住” ），然后规划下一步行动。这才是真正实用的人机交互！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503516525\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5731481481481482\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e25e2911&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicBLKeEFCnStqlc7nuRDNjs0e7UA7P1EfHaePAVmaibOVTzMKJI6LSDCRHmYMbGUiazgOQPsPSHuoYg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">场景五：AI 看懂 “专家会诊”！&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">医生一边滚动查看 CT 影像，一边用嘴说出诊断（“这里我们看到一些肺大疱和相关的纤维化改变...” ） 。OmniVinci 能同时 “看” CT 影像的动态变化 ，并 “听” 懂医生的专业解说 ，准确回答 “肺部纹理随时间如何变化？” 这类高难度问题，在医疗 AI 上大展身手 ！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503516526\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.787962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c76297ce&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicBLKeEFCnStqlc7nuRDNjs9Wsmcmwia2hEMMtGh2ia428UJlum3N1y1UvtD2nQHNibuKiaZuzrOEyOIg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">场景六：AI “全能解说” 体育比赛！&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">看网球比赛，AI 不再是 “睁眼瞎”。OmniVinci 能同步理解激烈的视觉动作（谁在发球、谁赢了这一分）和解说员的评论。在预测得分结果和回合长度上，它完胜 Qwen2.5-Omni。更重要的是，量化后在消费级显卡 GeForce RTX 4090 上它延迟极低，完全可以用于电视直播！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503516527\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.39166666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3f0c5a74&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicBLKeEFCnStqlc7nuRDNjsAQ4Q9kavufgF43UgGiaR1yA1cviaFxZWibiaBSvoof17XhwIKhM3cYolLw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503516528\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.29444444444444445\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1affdd10&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicBLKeEFCnStqlc7nuRDNjsacXdObA5GFUYnyboXcC5nexxJYSgln13Ugd0WLDBnFze5rBNenav3w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这不就是贾维斯吗？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">写在最后</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">OmniVinci 的出现，可能不仅仅是一个新 SOTA 9B 全模态模型的诞生，它更代表了一种全新的 AI 范式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">未来，AI 不再是割裂的 “视觉模型” 或 “音频模型”，而是统一的 “全模态感知系统”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">更低的训练成本，意味着更快的迭代和更广泛的应用。从能听懂指令的机器人，到能理解医生口述和 CT 影像的医疗 AI，再到监控异常声音和画面的智能工厂，一个更智能的未来，正在加速到来。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">英伟达这次，又交出了一份惊艳的答卷。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">对于 OmniVinci，你怎么看？你最期待它被用在什么地方？欢迎在评论区留下你的 “神预言”！&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "英伟达开源了 OmniVinci 全模态大模型，通过架构创新和数据引擎，实现视觉、音频、语言的统一理解，并在多模态任务上表现卓越。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "英伟达开源了 OmniVinci 全模态大模型，通过架构创新和数据引擎，实现视觉、音频、语言的统一理解，并在多模态任务上表现卓越。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了英伟达开源的 OmniVinci 全模态大语言模型，该模型通过 OmniAlignNet、Temporal Embedding Grouping 和 Constrained Rotary Time Embedding 三大架构创新，实现了视觉、音频、语言在同一潜空间中的深度统一理解。OmniVinci 在多项多模态基准测试中超越竞品，且训练数据量更少。文章还展示了 OmniVinci 在联合视听感知、语音交互、机器人控制、医疗 AI 和体育解说等多个真实场景中的强大应用潜力，预示着 AI 向全模态感知系统发展的新范式。模型已开源，提供论文和代码地址。",
